item.title: Emirates launches new route connecting Dubai with Yinchuan and Zhengzhou
item.description:
Emirates airline is increasing its commitment to China by starting a new service from Dubai to Yinchuan and Zhengzhou, two rapidly developing cities in Midwest China. This addition brings Emirates’ total destinations in mainland China to five, including existing service to Beijing, Shanghai, and Guangzhou. Source; Emirates. Emirates’ Chairman and Chief Executive, HH Sheikh Ahmed bin Saeed Al Maktoum, along with other company executives and a delegation of UAE business leaders, were on the inaugural flight...
